						<summary>

						<p>Gift of land to Śī(Śrī)rāmapirāṉ Bhaṭṭaṉ <hi rend="italic">alias</hi> Periyakōyil Nambi by <hi rend="bold">Chaṭṭayaṉ,</hi> a <hi rend="italic">sēṉaibōga</hi> of <hi rend="bold">Bōgaya-Daṇḍanāyakar-Vallaiya Daṇḍanāyaka</hi> (vide No. 154 above) for his well-being. The details of the date viz., <hi rend="bold">23rd (22+1) year, Karkaṭaka, śu. 14, Mūla, Sunday</hi> regularly correspond to <hi rend="bold">A.D. 1238, June 27, Sunday ·91; ·48.</hi></p>						

